{"tid":2351050,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"分享夢境體驗（真夢）","createTime":"2021-01-03T00:56:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-03T12:28:34.000Z","uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e761355bdc8ecd61cabb88a54cf385e79d7144c2","tid":2351050,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T00:56:38.000Z","msg":"夢醒後 唔記得咗個夢<br />\n淨係記得最後嗰幕係：<br />\n許賢著住西裝戴黑超唔知做乜<br />\n<br />\n嗰陣覺得好似發咗個好好睇嘅夢<br />\n甚至可以用嚟寫劇本<br />\n但我醒唔起 勁可惜 勁嘥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但一挈開張被 就突然諗返一個細節<br />\n之後由嗰個細節又諗返起好多其他嘅細節<br />\n<br />\n發現原來個夢都冇乜大不了<br />\n啲劇情斷到飛起<br />\n啲有趣位 同傷心位 淨係我自己先會明<br />\n嘥晒我啲記憶力<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇人有類似經歷？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d18f1daf4a69b5be0f2b946770eacd4ff78b66d","tid":2351050,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T00:57:19.000Z","msg":"屌我寫乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未瞓醒 瞓多陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af0dea2906705e344d8be88fec8a3e11f3fa9ef","tid":2351050,"uid":30836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T00:58:29.000Z","msg":"蓮囝幾開返個夢境臺？<br />\n等大家分享下自己嘅夢境<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4684413cffba8b31f77dd8859d0214cd8b8b0f5","tid":2351050,"uid":308264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T00:59:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0620da07504bd5eeb327cab696f866bf76755ce5","tid":2351050,"uid":107571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T01:07:11.000Z","msg":"之前發夢見到自己同一個唔識嘅女人結婚<br />\n<br />\n仲要係外國教堂 無請到人觀禮 得見證同埋證婚人<br />\n<br />\n行完禮之後就醒咗<br />\n<br />\n醒咗仲記得個夢 但諗唔起個女人嘅樣係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6a1b3ffef74716ea1e7cc6d6380967992002de","tid":2351050,"uid":35746,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score"